1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 24=

4
00:00:22,320 --> 00:00:23,000
Who's there?

5
00:00:35,280 --> 00:00:36,079
Father...

6
00:00:37,359 --> 00:00:38,840
You're from the Demon Sect?

7
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:45,399
Father.

8
00:00:46,159 --> 00:00:46,799
Father!

9
00:00:49,320 --> 00:00:51,840
Now that you've seen everything,

10
00:00:53,119 --> 00:00:54,799
there's no point in hiding it anymore.

11
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:57,640
Father, you're the leader
of the Martial Arts Alliance,

12
00:00:58,399 --> 00:01:00,359
respected by martial artists everywhere.

13
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:02,679
Why are you in league
with the Demon Sect?

14
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:03,799
Bingqing,

15
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:07,840
being the Martial Arts Alliance Leader
means nothing.

16
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:10,439
I will become the Martial God

17
00:01:10,959 --> 00:01:12,920
and make the entire martial world

18
00:01:13,439 --> 00:01:15,400
bow to the Murong family.

19
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,359
Father.

20
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:29,439
I've never asked you for anything,

21
00:01:30,079 --> 00:01:31,280
but I'm begging you now.

22
00:01:32,480 --> 00:01:34,359
Please spare Peng Dasheng.

23
00:01:35,239 --> 00:01:36,959
Please have mercy, Father.

24
00:01:37,359 --> 00:01:38,280
Get up.

25
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:42,200
I said, get up!

26
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,359
Bingqing,

27
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,640
after everything that's happened,

28
00:01:46,799 --> 00:01:49,000
you still can't forget that brat?

29
00:01:49,799 --> 00:01:50,640
Don't you know

30
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:51,840
he has

31
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:53,760
no feelings for you?

32
00:01:58,079 --> 00:01:59,519
I'd never fallen for anyone before.

33
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:02,040
Dasheng is the only one.

34
00:02:03,879 --> 00:02:05,079
He doesn't love me.

35
00:02:05,799 --> 00:02:07,200
His heart belongs to someone else.

36
00:02:07,879 --> 00:02:08,960
I've accepted all that.

37
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,199
Please spare his life, Father.

38
00:02:11,199 --> 00:02:11,520
Enough!

39
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,280
Please, Father...

40
00:02:14,879 --> 00:02:16,960
I won't let you
humiliate yourself like this.

41
00:02:17,599 --> 00:02:18,400
Bingqing,

42
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,479
come to your senses.

43
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,120
Look at yourself.

44
00:02:22,319 --> 00:02:24,039
Just look at what you've become.

45
00:02:24,199 --> 00:02:26,360
You're not acting like a Murong.

46
00:02:29,039 --> 00:02:30,439
Guards. Guards!

47
00:02:30,719 --> 00:02:30,960
Father!

48
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,400
Take her back to her room

49
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:33,560
and keep her under close watch.

50
00:02:33,879 --> 00:02:35,039
Without my permission,

51
00:02:35,439 --> 00:02:37,159
she is not to step outside.

52
00:02:37,159 --> 00:02:37,960
Please, Father!

53
00:02:38,039 --> 00:02:38,719
Go!

54
00:02:38,759 --> 00:02:39,639
You can't do this!

55
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:41,439
Father, you can't!

56
00:02:41,479 --> 00:02:42,000
Father!

57
00:02:42,159 --> 00:02:43,360
If she gets out...

58
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,080
Father!

59
00:02:44,199 --> 00:02:44,840
I'll have all your heads!

60
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,680
Please!

61
00:02:45,879 --> 00:02:46,680
Father!

62
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,840
(The Yellow Emperor's Inner Canon
states)

63
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:56,240
(that the human body
has Eight Extraordinary Meridians.)

64
00:02:56,319 --> 00:02:57,000
(They are)

65
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:59,280
(the Governor, Conception,
Thoroughfare, and Belt Vessels,)

66
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:02,199
(and the Yin Link, Yang Link,
Yin Heel and Yang Heel Vessels.)

67
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,560
(These eight meridians)

68
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:05,120
(lie outside
the regular meridian system,)

69
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:07,280
(hence the name
Eight Extraordinary Meridians.)

70
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:09,560
(They serve as reservoirs
of Qi and blood)

71
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:11,120
(and connect the entire body.)

72
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:16,520
Strange. This is truly strange.

73
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:18,840
What's wrong, Changsheng?

74
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:22,240
When I channeled Qi
to protect you just now,

75
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:24,520
I found
all eight of your meridians open.

76
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:26,439
And they show signs
of reaching perfect completion.

77
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,599
But normally,

78
00:03:28,719 --> 00:03:30,120
with sealed meridians from birth

79
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:32,280
and spiritual power trapped inside you,

80
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:34,560
you should be
little more than a living corpse.

81
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:36,479
Yet you're perfectly fine,

82
00:03:36,479 --> 00:03:38,879
and your inner energy flows more freely

83
00:03:38,879 --> 00:03:40,199
than an ordinary person's.

84
00:03:40,199 --> 00:03:42,479
It makes no sense.

85
00:03:42,479 --> 00:03:43,639
Are you sure you didn't get it wrong?

86
00:03:43,639 --> 00:03:44,639
Impossible.

87
00:03:44,639 --> 00:03:47,439
Your extraordinary meridians
are unlike anyone else's.

88
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:49,520
There's only one explanation.

89
00:04:00,719 --> 00:04:02,520
Just as I thought.

90
00:04:02,759 --> 00:04:07,120
Master, your Formless Sea of Qi
flows against your meridians.

91
00:04:07,159 --> 00:04:10,919
It came into contact with the pure
spiritual power in your soul jade.

92
00:04:10,919 --> 00:04:13,120
The two forces became intertwined

93
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,159
and somehow broke the seal

94
00:04:14,159 --> 00:04:17,639
on your meridians.

95
00:04:17,639 --> 00:04:19,680
It must be heaven's will.

96
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:20,800
You mean

97
00:04:21,399 --> 00:04:22,879
my sealed meridians are open?

98
00:04:22,879 --> 00:04:23,600
Exactly.

99
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:26,720
During your fight
with the Luocha Blade Demon,

100
00:04:26,839 --> 00:04:29,199
you unleashed all the spiritual power
inside you.

101
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,279
Only then

102
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,079
could it merge

103
00:04:31,079 --> 00:04:33,560
with your Formless Sea of Qi

104
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,160
and break through

105
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:36,920
the final blockage
in your eight meridians.

106
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:39,079
You truly found life at death's door.

107
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:51,079
Life at death's door...

108
00:04:51,959 --> 00:04:54,399
(Within death lies the spark of life.)

109
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,040
(Only through death can one live.)

110
00:04:56,519 --> 00:05:00,240
(Whether the path ahead
is a blessing or a trial,)

111
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:04,240
(only you can walk it and find out.)

112
00:05:04,879 --> 00:05:06,279
Within death lies the spark of life.

113
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,720
Only through death can one be reborn.

114
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,439
So Master had already told me

115
00:05:09,439 --> 00:05:10,600
how to change my fate.

116
00:05:11,879 --> 00:05:13,680
What do you mean?

117
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:14,879
Master once told me

118
00:05:15,279 --> 00:05:16,480
that a destined tribulation
cannot be changed,

119
00:05:16,759 --> 00:05:18,639
but even within it
lies a chance to live.

120
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,279
To defy heaven and change my fate,

121
00:05:20,639 --> 00:05:21,480
I must risk death,

122
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,439
go all in,

123
00:05:22,439 --> 00:05:23,759
break free of my shackles,

124
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:24,800
and rewrite my destiny.

125
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:27,040
I understand now.

126
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,240
The Dao teaches

127
00:05:28,399 --> 00:05:30,399
that without surviving tribulation
and overcoming adversity,

128
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:32,240
one cannot forge a true Dao Heart.

129
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:35,160
That's exactly what you meant.

130
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:37,240
Your master paved your path long ago.

131
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:39,240
He was waiting for you
to realize it yourself.

132
00:05:47,079 --> 00:05:47,839
A red light is piercing the sky

133
00:05:47,839 --> 00:05:49,040
from Gen in the northeast.

134
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:51,160
Master, what kind of omen is that?

135
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:53,319
This is the Red Gen Omen.

136
00:05:53,319 --> 00:05:55,839
It appears only once in a century,
when the heavens open.

137
00:05:56,519 --> 00:05:57,959
What does it mean?

138
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,199
Is it good or bad?

139
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:03,000
Gen represents the mountain
and signifies stillness.

140
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,839
Red represents fire
and signifies change.

141
00:06:04,959 --> 00:06:06,199
When the two forces collide,

142
00:06:06,199 --> 00:06:07,519
there are two possible outcomes.

143
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:09,519
If fire consumes the mountain,

144
00:06:09,519 --> 00:06:11,079
a heavenly calamity will descend,

145
00:06:11,079 --> 00:06:12,480
and countless lives will perish.

146
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:15,199
But if the mountain contains the spark,

147
00:06:15,199 --> 00:06:16,680
all things will be renewed,

148
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,160
and the old order
will give way to the new.

149
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,199
Could it be...

150
00:06:27,879 --> 00:06:30,279
I knew the Red Gen Omen

151
00:06:30,279 --> 00:06:32,000
couldn't have appeared for no reason.

152
00:06:32,319 --> 00:06:35,639
So that brat
is about to attain enlightenment.

153
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:36,480
Master,

154
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:39,839
since you knew
Peng's fate could be changed,

155
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,920
why didn't you just tell him?

156
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:47,360
The Dao cannot be taught.
He must realize it himself.

157
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,720
Just as this omen
has two possible meanings,

158
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,319
whether it brings fortune or disaster

159
00:06:51,519 --> 00:06:54,079
depends on the one
whose fate it foretells.

160
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:57,279
Now that the Red Gen Omen has appeared,

161
00:06:58,279 --> 00:07:01,839
Dasheng's path to the Dao
has truly begun.

162
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:04,360
Whether he succeeds or fails,

163
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:07,879
he must walk it himself.

164
00:07:12,199 --> 00:07:14,639
Master, I just don't understand.

165
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:17,439
Now that your sealed meridians are open,

166
00:07:17,439 --> 00:07:19,399
why aren't you returning to the sect?

167
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:22,879
My master taught me
to stay true to my heart.

168
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,319
But only today
did I understand what that means.

169
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:26,839
Staying true to my heart

170
00:07:28,199 --> 00:07:30,240
doesn't mean hiding in the sect
and living in peace.

171
00:07:30,639 --> 00:07:32,360
It means standing firm
in what you know is right.

172
00:07:34,319 --> 00:07:35,319
Heaven gave me

173
00:07:35,319 --> 00:07:36,839
another chance

174
00:07:37,079 --> 00:07:38,279
and unsealed my meridians.

175
00:07:39,279 --> 00:07:40,439
So I can't shirk my duty.

176
00:07:42,079 --> 00:07:44,800
Saving the people from such suffering

177
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:47,680
will be a long and difficult road.

178
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:49,240
The martial world is dangerous now,

179
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,439
especially with the Demon Sect

180
00:07:50,439 --> 00:07:52,199
more vicious than ever.

181
00:07:52,439 --> 00:07:54,240
Don't act recklessly.

182
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,759
Be careful at every step

183
00:07:55,759 --> 00:07:57,319
and plan before you act.

184
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,040
Any news?

185
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,399
We just received word.

186
00:08:05,519 --> 00:08:08,000
Murong Xiang has led the sect leaders

187
00:08:08,199 --> 00:08:09,240
and their disciples out of Gusu.

188
00:08:09,519 --> 00:08:10,399
They should reach the Demon Sect's lair

189
00:08:10,399 --> 00:08:12,000
at the Busi Sea in seven days.

190
00:08:14,399 --> 00:08:16,000
That's faster than I expected.

191
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,199
It seems Master Baiyi

192
00:08:17,439 --> 00:08:18,600
is getting impatient.

193
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:20,759
Peng Dasheng, I don't understand.

194
00:08:21,199 --> 00:08:22,800
Those sect leaders betrayed you

195
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,079
and banished you from the martial world.

196
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:25,319
Why are you still helping them?

197
00:08:25,319 --> 00:08:27,279
Yeah, I don't understand either.

198
00:08:28,399 --> 00:08:29,639
I'm not helping them.

199
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,279
I'm doing this for the countless

200
00:08:31,279 --> 00:08:32,600
martial artists
who still stand by the martial way.

201
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:34,360
If Master Baiyi succeeds,

202
00:08:34,759 --> 00:08:36,080
the martial world
will never know peace again.

203
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:37,720
More people like Xiaojiu

204
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:38,879
and your master

205
00:08:38,879 --> 00:08:40,399
will die at the Demon Sect's hands.

206
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,759
I can't

207
00:08:41,759 --> 00:08:42,679
let that happen again.

208
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:48,159
You seem like a different person.

209
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:50,639
You used to stay out
of the martial world's feuds.

210
00:08:50,679 --> 00:08:52,279
All you cared about
was your Master and your sect.

211
00:08:52,559 --> 00:08:55,080
Now you're willing to risk everything

212
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:56,320
for everyone else.

213
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:57,919
Is this really you?

214
00:09:00,759 --> 00:09:02,120
My Master always said,

215
00:09:02,519 --> 00:09:03,519
"The smallest thing can hold a world,

216
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,559
and the small reveals the whole."

217
00:09:04,559 --> 00:09:05,919
I was born with sealed meridians.

218
00:09:05,919 --> 00:09:07,840
Every turning point in my life

219
00:09:07,879 --> 00:09:09,279
was like fighting against the current.

220
00:09:09,519 --> 00:09:10,679
Nothing ever came easily.

221
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:12,840
But those hardships

222
00:09:13,519 --> 00:09:14,840
taught me how precious every life is.

223
00:09:14,919 --> 00:09:16,000
Whether it's for others

224
00:09:16,399 --> 00:09:17,519
or for myself,

225
00:09:17,639 --> 00:09:18,240
this is the Dao

226
00:09:19,159 --> 00:09:20,279
I must attain on my own.

227
00:09:34,159 --> 00:09:35,200
What are you doing here?

228
00:09:35,679 --> 00:09:37,039
For something
as big as saving the world,

229
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,120
you can't leave us out.

230
00:09:38,519 --> 00:09:39,279
Whoa, hold it.

231
00:09:39,279 --> 00:09:40,519
I'm not as noble as you.

232
00:09:40,639 --> 00:09:42,639
I'm only here for Dasheng

233
00:09:42,879 --> 00:09:44,559
and to see what kind of place

234
00:09:44,559 --> 00:09:45,759
the Busi Sea really is.

235
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,679
How come you two seem

236
00:09:48,679 --> 00:09:51,000
a lot friendlier

237
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,039
since coming back from Liuchu Manor?

238
00:09:53,679 --> 00:09:54,480
Do we?

239
00:09:55,399 --> 00:09:56,720
Someone once raced me

240
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:57,320
and somehow rode his horse

241
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,960
straight into a vegetable stall.

242
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,559
It cost him three taels to settle it.

243
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,200
Really shameless.

244
00:10:02,279 --> 00:10:04,000
Still better than showing off
on horseback to impress a girl

245
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,360
and nearly ending up in the river.

246
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,360
If I hadn't grabbed you in time,

247
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:08,639
you would've been soaked to the bone.

248
00:10:09,279 --> 00:10:10,360
And you still have the nerve
to make fun of me?

249
00:10:10,399 --> 00:10:10,840
Pretty boy,

250
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:11,399
you'd better watch it.

251
00:10:11,519 --> 00:10:12,600
My horse got spooked, okay?

252
00:10:13,039 --> 00:10:13,480
It got spooked!

253
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:14,279
Don't you get it?

254
00:10:14,279 --> 00:10:16,000
Enough. Let's go.

255
00:10:29,519 --> 00:10:31,159
Master Murong,

256
00:10:31,159 --> 00:10:33,320
our vanguard has breached
the Demon Sect's lair at the Busi Sea.

257
00:10:33,519 --> 00:10:34,879
The Demon Sect fled at the sight of us.

258
00:10:34,879 --> 00:10:35,519
They barely put up a fight.

259
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:36,320
Keep scouting.

260
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:36,840
Yes.

261
00:10:38,159 --> 00:10:40,159
Amitabha.

262
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,759
Master Murong,

263
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:44,240
the Demon Sect has been entrenched

264
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:46,000
at the Busi Sea for decades.

265
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,679
Though it has declined in recent years,

266
00:10:47,799 --> 00:10:50,360
a sect with such deep roots

267
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:51,759
wouldn't collapse so easily.

268
00:10:51,759 --> 00:10:53,840
How could
they have been routed so quickly?

269
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:57,360
I believe this is a trap.

270
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:22,000
I am Qiu Bin,
leader of the Qingcheng Sect.

271
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:23,879
Today, I will deliver heaven's justice

272
00:11:23,879 --> 00:11:26,039
and cut you two fiends to pieces!

273
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:38,840
You...

274
00:11:39,399 --> 00:11:41,200
I thought you were
some great martial master.

275
00:11:41,559 --> 00:11:43,000
Turns out you're just a weakling.

276
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:45,240
Demon Sect disciples, hear me!

277
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:47,000
Kill them all!

278
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:48,159
Leave no one alive!

279
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:51,519
Kill them!

280
00:11:56,799 --> 00:11:58,360
Fellow sect leaders!

281
00:11:58,759 --> 00:12:00,320
- Master Murong.
- Get their leader first.

282
00:12:00,559 --> 00:12:02,559
Everyone, follow me to the Busi Sea.

283
00:12:02,679 --> 00:12:04,039
We'll kill Master Baiyi!

284
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,000
Go!

285
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:24,679
No! It's a trap!

286
00:12:28,879 --> 00:12:30,320
Fools.

287
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:34,480
You thought a handful of weaklings
could destroy my sect?

288
00:12:34,759 --> 00:12:36,159
You overestimate yourselves.

289
00:12:37,399 --> 00:12:37,879
You...

290
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:40,679
You're from the Demon Sect?

291
00:12:40,759 --> 00:12:42,120
More precisely,

292
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:45,799
I'm Master Baiyi, the one
you've all been so eager to kill.

293
00:12:53,380 --> 00:12:53,860
♪Come on♪

294
00:12:57,380 --> 00:12:59,060
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

295
00:13:01,020 --> 00:13:03,980
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

296
00:13:04,260 --> 00:13:07,180
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

297
00:13:07,420 --> 00:13:10,260
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

298
00:13:10,660 --> 00:13:13,260
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

299
00:13:13,780 --> 00:13:16,740
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

300
00:13:16,980 --> 00:13:19,980
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

301
00:13:20,140 --> 00:13:23,060
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

302
00:13:23,220 --> 00:13:25,980
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

303
00:13:26,540 --> 00:13:29,860
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

304
00:13:29,900 --> 00:13:32,900
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

305
00:13:32,940 --> 00:13:38,580
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

306
00:13:38,980 --> 00:13:41,020
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

307
00:13:41,580 --> 00:13:44,100
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

308
00:13:44,820 --> 00:13:47,220
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

309
00:13:47,340 --> 00:13:51,020
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

310
00:13:51,620 --> 00:13:53,740
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

311
00:13:54,660 --> 00:13:56,780
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

312
00:13:56,940 --> 00:14:00,220
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

313
00:14:00,260 --> 00:14:04,540
♪I am my own king♪

314
00:14:17,620 --> 00:14:19,180
♪I emerge into the world♪

315
00:14:19,180 --> 00:14:20,940
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

316
00:14:20,940 --> 00:14:22,300
♪My pride is my trump card♪

317
00:14:22,300 --> 00:14:24,100
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

318
00:14:24,100 --> 00:14:25,500
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

319
00:14:25,500 --> 00:14:27,260
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

320
00:14:27,260 --> 00:14:28,780
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

321
00:14:28,780 --> 00:14:30,500
♪I dare to break every rule♪

322
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:31,820
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

323
00:14:31,820 --> 00:14:33,660
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

324
00:14:33,660 --> 00:14:34,900
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

325
00:14:34,900 --> 00:14:37,140
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

326
00:14:37,140 --> 00:14:38,660
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

327
00:14:38,660 --> 00:14:40,260
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

328
00:14:40,260 --> 00:14:41,860
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

329
00:14:41,860 --> 00:14:43,580
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

330
00:14:43,580 --> 00:14:45,300
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

331
00:14:45,300 --> 00:14:46,660
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

332
00:14:46,660 --> 00:14:48,300
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

333
00:14:48,300 --> 00:14:49,780
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

334
00:14:49,780 --> 00:14:51,500
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

335
00:14:51,500 --> 00:14:53,100
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

336
00:14:53,100 --> 00:14:54,660
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

337
00:14:54,660 --> 00:14:58,980
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

338
00:14:58,980 --> 00:15:01,140
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

339
00:15:01,140 --> 00:15:03,740
♪Let me write the legend♪

340
00:15:08,620 --> 00:15:11,180
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

341
00:15:11,180 --> 00:15:14,500
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

342
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:16,980
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

343
00:15:16,980 --> 00:15:21,060
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

344
00:15:21,420 --> 00:15:24,020
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

345
00:15:24,140 --> 00:15:26,500
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

346
00:15:26,500 --> 00:15:29,540
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

347
00:15:29,540 --> 00:15:34,580
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
